posts.name: icemannie
posts.cooked:
You should be running gamepad operations out of Robot Container, not out of the Swerve Subsystem periodic. driveToPose is also running in SwerveSubsystem periodic. It only gets 20ms to run and should only have the odometry and vision updates.

In RobotContainer it could look something like

drivebase.driverXbox.leftTrigger() .onTrue( Commands.defer(() → Commands.runOnce(() → drivebase.findClosestAprilTag()), Set.of(drivebase))) .whileTrue(Commands.defer(() → drivebase.driveToPose(drivebase.reefFinalPose), Set.of(drivebase))); findClosestAprilTag and subsequent code would put its result into a Pose2d reefFinalPose
